Class ImageAppResourceExistenceBOMImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.ctm.bom.BusinessObjectModuleImpl

        • curam.util.ctm.bom.resources.impl.ImageAppResourceExistenceBOMImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BusinessObjectModule, ExistenceBOM

    public class ImageAppResourceExistenceBOMImpl
extends AppResourceExistenceBOMImpl
    This is the Existence Business Object Module implementation for an AppResource BOM. A resource BOM consists of the resource in the specified locale, or any locale if none is specified. This class determines if an AppResource BOM exists on the target system.
